{"tid":2050938,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記者遭美警射擊 外長要求美方解釋並追責 同時指美國計劃動用軍隊鎖壓和平示威是火上加油","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T15:37:53.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb1dc7f913fc84f61cf389d42dd0d802fc32048","tid":2050938,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1787842/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A-%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%A6%E8%BF%BD%E8%B2%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1787842%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B2%25AC&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY%2FroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=8531bc8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1787842%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25B2%25AC&h=2730d09d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1787842/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A-%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%A6%E8%BF%BD%E8%B2%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n黑人男子弗洛伊德懷疑被警員跪頸致死事件，引發大規模示威，美國部分警方處理示威的手法被質疑濫用暴力，就連其他國家的記者也遭殃。<br />\n<br />\n日前，《德國之聲》的記者及攝影師在美遭襲一事在德國國內引發關注。在報道中稱，《德國之聲》一個報道團隊5月30日和31日兩天在美國明尼阿波利斯報道當地抗議示威期間，兩度遭到美國警察阻止。該台記者拍攝的現場畫面顯示，儘管多次表明記者身份，他們仍遭到警方布袋彈射擊並被威脅拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯周三（3日）針對德國之聲記者日前在明尼蘇達報道抗議時兩度遭美國警方開槍警告一事，馬斯對此表示譴責並要求美方予以解釋並追責。「不能只是受到批評，更必須受到追責和解釋澄清」只有這樣，記者的工作才能有效地得到保護。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯又批評美國總統特朗普日前威脅動用軍隊平息示威的言論是在「火上加油」，指威脅使用暴力只會引發更多的暴力。「我們必須尋求和解，而非火上加油。我們應當肩並肩共同對抗極端分子，而非讓彼此走向割裂。」"},{"pid":"b3a8bcb73ddedb1e77a37127200b9c7e7aa43056","tid":2050938,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35b7a23508ec2a8359435287c546fd22d7a20a7","tid":2050938,"uid":264245,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"新聞報d唔報d<br />\n有looting唔提，破壞文物唔提"},{"pid":"a43b8c8bcbdbab8fe82d2f8e2f1f28ff022167c3","tid":2050938,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"$0.5"},{"pid":"91d028347e937c1def0f248365351093ebd2ba93","tid":2050938,"uid":13745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:17:29.000Z","msg":"香港黑警打盲記者又唔見佢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61e676fdecf71fb7d973a6028971b3628d7c118","tid":2050938,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"德國外長只敢屌文明國家"},{"pid":"edf87ec464b6398726437042ba654020e74a104f","tid":2050938,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b61e676fdecf71fb7d973a6028971b3628d7c118","tid":2050938,"uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"德國外長只敢屌文明國家"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢唔係接見左G